<span class="time">November 8, 2013 6:40 pm</span></p>
<h1>Barometer: home life technology<span class='ftbf-syndicationIndicator' data-uuid='afd0ade4-4743-11e3-b4d3-00144feabdc0'></span></h1>
<p class="byline ">
<span>By Esther Jane Odida</span></p>
</div>
<script>FT.$doc.trigger("pgObjStop", {key: "8"});</script>
<script>FT.$doc.trigger("pgObjStart", {key: "9", keyType: "el"});</script>
<div class="fullstory fullstoryBody specialArticle" data-comp-name="fullstory" data-comp-view="fullstory" data-comp-index="1" data-timer-key="9">
<div class="standfirst">
An extra touch of tech for smarter living
</div>
<div id="storyContent"><div class="fullstoryImage fullstoryImageHybrid article" style="width:600px"><span class="story-image"><img alt="home life tech accessories" src="http://im.ft-static.com/content/images/85491a7f-ca82-4fdc-aea5-8026ac9e6ecb.img" /></span><p class="caption">Clockwise from top: Sage smart kettle, Parrot ‘Flower Power’, Lapka sensors, Goji smart lock and Zapi UV toothbrush sanitiser</p></div><p><strong>Zapi UV toothbrush sanitiser</strong>
</p>
<p>A toothbrush holder that claims to kill germs in six minutes. £24.99; <a href="http://www.firebox.com/" target="_blank">firebox.com</a>
</p>
<p><strong>. . .</strong>
</p>
<p><strong>Sage smart kettle</strong>
</p>
<div class="insideArticleShare"><ul><!----></ul></div><div class="story-package" data-track-comp-name="moreOn"><div class="insideArticleCompHeader"><h3 class="insideArticleCompHeaderTitle">More</h3></div><h4>IN Pursuits</h4><ul><li data-track-pos="0"> <a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/24f96668-3ec1-11e4-adef-00144feabdc0.html">Running with the FT: Malcolm Gladwell</a></li><li data-track-pos="1"> <a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/0961fd7a-330e-11e4-93c6-00144feabdc0.html">Chess grandmaster class – Nigel Short v Sol Campbell</a></li><li data-track-pos="2"> <a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/6f232e2a-2d7a-11e4-8105-00144feabdc0.html">How to fly a fighter jet with the FT</a></li><li data-track-pos="3"> <a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/1b8b687c-1209-11e4-a17a-00144feabdc0.html">The Pursuits Interview – Laura Trott</a></li></ul></div><p>This kettle from Heston Blumenthal’s range has five temperature settings for optimal tea flavour. £99.99; <a href="http://www.sageappliances.co.uk/" target="_blank">sageappliances.co.uk</a>
</p>
